"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eww1719683180873.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eww1719683180873.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eww1719683180873.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qfg1665702596984\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__set_239153\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">1</span> (<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__topic_d77129e1_d77130e1_d77131e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__p_d77132e1_d77133e1_d77134e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__section_w2194ab1b7b5_w2195ab1b7_w2196ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__p_d77135e1_d77136e1_d77137e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">set $fieldcheck</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__topic_d50697e1_d50698e1_d50699e1_d50700e1_d50701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d564049e83\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20__entry__2\">Literal </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__d6481e20__entry__3\"> ProcScript function</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__topic_d50702e1_d50703e1_d50704e1_d50705e1_d50706e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d564049e137\">Return Values </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> cannot be used with\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qfg1665702596984__table_d7388e1_d7389e1_d7390e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var> was successfully reset.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__topic_d50707e1_d50708e1_d50709e1_d50710e1_d50711e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d564049e205\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__d6482e20\">Allowed in all component types except self-contained Report and Services.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__topic_d50712e1_d50713e1_d50714e1_d50715e1_d50716e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d564049e214\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__p_d77153e1_d77154e1_d77155e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> statement resets the value of the ProcScript function <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">0</span>). It can be used only with functions for which this feature is documented.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__section_ldv_m11_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d564049e235\">Example: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set $occcheck</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> to change the value of\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code> (<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>):</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qfg1665702596984__pre_oys_p11_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n; set $occcheck to TRUE to enable checking\n\n name = $1\n retrieve\n set $occcheck(INVOICE)\n edit NAME\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukk1665702596834.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>reset</a><p>Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420531\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420531\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; trans